<P>
The marriage of Sir Rudolf Bing to Carroll Douglass was ordered annulled 
Wednesday by a Manhattan Supreme Court judge after a trial in which Bing's 
court-appointed guardian claimed the former opera impresario suffers from 
Alzheimer's disease and was unaware that he had gotten married. 
</P>
