<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE TIMES EXPANDS BUSINESS COVERAGE IN SAN DIEGO COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Beginning today, The Times expands its San Diego business coverage by adding a 
second day of special pages for San Diego County each Thursday. New, regular 
features will focus on products developed by San Diego firms, personality 
profiles, and updates on key issues affecting the local business community. The 
San Diego County business pages also are published each Tuesday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
