<BYLINE>
<P>
By ALEENE MacMINN, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Add London and Brasilia to the world capitals that will be involved, along with 
Washington and Moscow, in ABC's next "Capital to Capital" live satellite 
broadcast series. The program, the fifth so far, will focus on global 
environment when it airs Tuesday from 11:30 p.m.-1 a.m. Peter Jennings anchors 
in this country. . . .ALEENE MacMINN 
