ADMINISTRATION (U.S.); NATIONAL INSTITUTES OF HEALTH; TRENDS; UNITED STATES -- 
HEALTH; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; PATIENTS RIGHTS; DISEASES; FAUCI, ANTHONY S 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
