discussion of plan. United Press International; Photo, Moment of hope -- 
President Bush holds up an infant at an inner-city Washington clinic where 
babies of addict mothers are treated. The visit was the start of an exhaustive 
campaign by Bush to sell his anti-drug plan to the nation. (Story on Page 14) 
Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
