</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Astalled truck blocked three lanes of the San Diego Freeway near Mulholland 
Drive Wednesday morning, backing up rush-hour traffic for several miles, the 
California Highway Patrol reported. 
</P>
<P>
No one was injured, but traffic was at a virtual standstill from Sepulveda Pass 
