Photo, COLOR, Johnel Turner, left, Tim Gutierrez and Jason Isaacs, right, ham 
it up in neighborhood where they grew up in Oxnard. The three high school 
quarterbacks begin their final season Friday. GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
