</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Clippers signed forward Michael Young, who played in Italy last season, and 
guard Fred Cofield, who played in Spain. 
</P>
