transition to a passing game last fall, will go after Carpinteria this fall. 
LAWRENCE K. HO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, An All-County pick last season, 
linebacker Lance Martin is expected to give the Thousand Oaks defense a lift. 
GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
